G28 ;HOME ALL AXES
M190 S25 ;WAIT FOR BED TO REACH TEMP
G1 Z150 F3000 ;MOVE Z AXIS UP 150 MM
G1 Y200 F3000 ;MOVE Y AXIS FORWARD 200 MM
M84 ;DISABLE STEPPERS
